

ng add @angular/elements => adds polyfills plus installs elements

tsconfig.json set target to es2015 or you have to add more polyfills

in module:
* remove bootstrap
* add elements to EntryComponents
* add ngOnBootstrap() to override bootstrapping
* in constructor, creatcustomelement

package.json, create new script that runs the build and concats the files
* output-hashing none will turn off hash naming
* --prod to get small bundle

custom elements can only take strings.  change grocery-list to accept items as a string